    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Private or civil injurious actions or breaches of duty, other than breaches of contract, intentional or not, for which the law will award a remedy in the form of damages.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
